1
00:01:05,599 --> 00:01:06,400
The car's here, the car's here!

2
00:01:06,400 --> 00:01:07,480
Here they come, get ready!

3
00:01:08,560 --> 00:01:09,359
Quick, get in position!

4
00:01:09,920 --> 00:01:12,439
Next up, the team from Frostwind City!

5
00:01:13,079 --> 00:01:14,840
Who will take the championship today?

6
00:01:17,319 --> 00:01:18,120
Look over here!

7
00:01:20,719 --> 00:01:22,040
We'll keep you updated.

8
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:28,799
Sir!

9
00:01:28,799 --> 00:01:30,640
What are your thoughts on today's match?

10
00:01:30,719 --> 00:01:31,760
Please, say a few words.

11
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:33,040
Just a couple of words, please.

12
00:01:33,040 --> 00:01:33,519
Say something, please.

13
00:01:33,519 --> 00:01:34,120
Just a few words.

14
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:34,640
Just a brief comment.

15
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:35,359
Come on!

16
00:01:37,519 --> 00:01:38,280
Hey, he's leaving?

17
00:01:39,319 --> 00:01:40,920
You can tell the competitors today

18
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:41,599
are all in excellent form.

19
00:01:41,599 --> 00:01:42,439
Stay tuned for our follow-up coverage.

20
00:01:42,439 --> 00:01:43,359
Let's wait and see!

21
00:01:45,480 --> 00:01:46,040
Come on, come on!

22
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:49,439
Young Master Liu, Young Master Liu!

23
00:01:49,439 --> 00:01:51,040
What are your thoughts on this

24
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:52,040
Path to Immortality tournament?

25
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:52,719
Me?

26
00:01:52,719 --> 00:01:54,599
Young Master Liu, any thoughts to share?

27
00:01:55,599 --> 00:01:56,640
This time around,

28
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:58,200
there's always only one goal,

29
00:01:58,480 --> 00:01:59,640
and that's the championship.

30
00:02:00,799 --> 00:02:03,040
Young Master Liu seems very confident.

31
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:05,239
You could say he's riding high.

32
00:02:06,079 --> 00:02:07,439
Since you're all done asking,

33
00:02:07,439 --> 00:02:08,639
let me say a little something.

34
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:10,479
Let me introduce myself.

35
00:02:10,599 --> 00:02:11,240
I am

36
00:02:11,439 --> 00:02:14,000
Liu Chengfeng of the Liu family, Shanhai City.

37
00:02:14,599 --> 00:02:16,800
We came to the Path to Immortality

38
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:19,560
mainly to promote various well-known brands.

39
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:21,199
As you can see, our advertising vehicle

40
00:02:21,439 --> 00:02:23,840
still has plenty of ad space available.

41
00:02:24,039 --> 00:02:25,360
We hope everyone will

42
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:26,960
eagerly partner up with us.

43
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:28,599
Come on, show it off.

44
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,719
Look, on this side here,

45
00:02:31,319 --> 00:02:32,240
the side, the back,

46
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:34,919
we've got ad space everywhere.

47
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:36,879
Looking forward to sincere cooperation.

48
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:38,039
Smile.

49
00:02:38,719 --> 00:02:39,840
Anything else you'd like to add?

50
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:40,520
You?

51
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:42,080
He's got nothing to add.

52
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:43,800
Like we always say,

53
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,840
we're not short on money,

54
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:48,560
just short on valuable partners.

55
00:02:49,439 --> 00:02:50,199
Liu Chengfeng!

56
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,000
That's me.

57
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:52,680
All right, that's it.

58
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:54,919
I'll be heading off now.

59
00:02:55,319 --> 00:02:56,599
Young Master Liu, my microphone!

60
00:02:57,319 --> 00:02:58,120
Look at you people.

61
00:02:58,439 --> 00:02:59,560
So small-minded.

62
00:02:59,719 --> 00:03:01,599
Fussing over a mere microphone, honestly.

63
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:04,120
People like this, who'd have thought.

64
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:06,800
Young Master Liu seems very confident.

65
00:03:06,919 --> 00:03:08,120
Let's wait and see!

66
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:19,159
Brother Su Yang!

67
00:03:19,719 --> 00:03:21,680
So this is the hotel in the Imperial Capital?

68
00:03:23,759 --> 00:03:25,080
It's so beautiful!

69
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:31,039
We've spent way too much time on the road.

70
00:03:31,159 --> 00:03:31,960
Let's hurry inside.

71
00:03:32,639 --> 00:03:33,039
Come on.

72
00:03:33,039 --> 00:03:33,599
Okay.

73
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:34,639
Be careful.

74
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:41,000
The men of Chuncao City are such cowards.

75
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:42,439
Pushing a woman out as their captain.

76
00:03:42,719 --> 00:03:44,080
Is Frostwind City any better?

77
00:03:44,159 --> 00:03:45,680
Their captain's a cripple too.

78
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:46,960
Qiushui City is real great.

79
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:47,960
They sent a kid.

80
00:03:48,639 --> 00:03:50,599
You folks from Shushan City are so cultured.

81
00:03:50,639 --> 00:03:51,800
Sending an old man over.

82
00:03:51,919 --> 00:03:53,280
Are you here to give us a lecture?

83
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:53,800
You...

84
00:03:58,159 --> 00:04:00,039
Why isn't anyone mocking Shanhai City?

85
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:01,520
Need you even ask?

86
00:04:02,439 --> 00:04:04,560
Obviously, Shanhai City is just too outstanding.

87
00:04:04,599 --> 00:04:06,759
Anyone's better than Shanhai City.

88
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,280
Their clothes are covered in ads.

89
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:09,400
Like they're desperate for cash.

90
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:10,080
Exactly.

91
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:11,879
No one's worse than Shanhai City.

92
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,120
Shanhai City.

93
00:04:13,159 --> 00:04:14,759
The shame of the eight main cities.

94
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:15,919
Right.

95
00:04:24,519 --> 00:04:26,399
The Imperial Capital just sent a notice.

96
00:04:26,879 --> 00:04:29,000
The eight main cities skip the qualifiers.

97
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:30,759
The other hundred cities battle for eight spots.

98
00:04:30,839 --> 00:04:32,600
Then each picks a main city to challenge.

99
00:04:33,160 --> 00:04:34,199
Winners advance.

100
00:04:34,199 --> 00:04:35,120
Losers are eliminated.

101
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:36,360
And the Imperial Capital?

102
00:04:38,160 --> 00:04:39,639
Only the final winning team

103
00:04:39,959 --> 00:04:41,399
gets to face the Imperial Capital.

104
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:42,920
That's not fair!

105
00:04:43,319 --> 00:04:44,680
In the face of true strength,

106
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,480
fairness doesn't even apply.

107
00:04:48,399 --> 00:04:49,279
Su Yang and the others are here.

108
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:58,639
You came just in time.

109
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:01,360
We don't have to do the qualifiers.

110
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:02,680
No more qualifiers.

111
00:05:03,639 --> 00:05:04,399
Then let's go out and have fun.

112
00:05:04,959 --> 00:05:05,680
Didn't you say there were

113
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:06,839
some great scenic spots nearby?

114
00:05:06,959 --> 00:05:07,720
Come on, let's go!

115
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:08,480
Hold on a moment.

116
00:05:09,879 --> 00:05:10,920
There's something

117
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,079
I need to discuss with you alone.

118
00:05:15,759 --> 00:05:17,480
We'll go take a stroll then.

119
00:05:20,879 --> 00:05:21,480
Let's go.

120
00:05:23,519 --> 00:05:24,720
You go out too.

121
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:38,319
According to the latest ancient texts we've found,

122
00:05:38,879 --> 00:05:41,199
the immortal spirit energy filling the world

123
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:43,680
actually belongs to the immortals.

124
00:05:44,199 --> 00:05:46,000
So it carries with it

125
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,879
all sorts of subtle differences.

126
00:05:48,199 --> 00:05:49,279
And these emotions

127
00:05:49,639 --> 00:05:51,759
will affect our own consciousness,

128
00:05:52,279 --> 00:05:54,040
amplifying one particular emotion

129
00:05:54,199 --> 00:05:55,439
without limit.

130
00:05:55,879 --> 00:05:57,079
In other words,

131
00:05:57,519 --> 00:05:58,800
someone already impatient

132
00:05:58,879 --> 00:06:00,240
will become more violent.

133
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:02,040
Someone already stubborn

134
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:03,720
will become more obsessive.

135
00:06:03,879 --> 00:06:05,959
A cheapskate like you

136
00:06:06,079 --> 00:06:06,959
will become even cheaper.

137
00:06:08,319 --> 00:06:09,759
Idiots get more idiotic,

138
00:06:10,319 --> 00:06:11,519
and I'll get even crazier.

139
00:06:11,519 --> 00:06:13,360
Can you be a bit more serious?

140
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:15,120
What we're discussing right now

141
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:17,279
could decide the peace of our future.

142
00:06:17,279 --> 00:06:19,240
Why talk peace with a madman?

143
00:06:19,879 --> 00:06:21,480
Are you asking me to save the world?

144
00:06:21,839 --> 00:06:23,319
For justice, for peace,

145
00:06:23,319 --> 00:06:24,240
sacrificing myself?

146
00:06:24,319 --> 00:06:25,920
That's stuff you only see on TV,

147
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:28,000
made specifically for kids.

148
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:31,800
Why do you keep emphasizing kids?

149
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:34,160
Because once you grow up,

150
00:06:34,279 --> 00:06:35,480
you naturally stop believing it.

151
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,959
I'm just teaming up with you

152
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:40,959
to win a prize.

153
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:42,480
Don't tell me you think

154
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,839
I've actually become Captain Lingxiao.

155
00:06:47,439 --> 00:06:48,120
At most,

156
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:49,519
I promise

157
00:06:49,839 --> 00:06:51,120
I won't turn into one of those TV show

158
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:52,600
villains belching black smoke.

159
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:53,399
All right,

160
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:55,079
if there's nothing else, I'm off.

161
00:06:56,839 --> 00:06:57,439
Oh, right.

162
00:06:58,160 --> 00:06:59,560
Unless someone's dying,

163
00:06:59,759 --> 00:07:00,720
don't call me.

164
00:07:01,279 --> 00:07:02,160
Wait a second.

165
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:06,120
In a moment, the team captains from each city

166
00:07:06,399 --> 00:07:07,600
have to attend the check-in ceremony.

167
00:07:08,639 --> 00:07:09,439
Once we've taken photos

168
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:10,800
and the ceremony's over, you can leave.

169
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:12,360
Tell me,

170
00:07:12,839 --> 00:07:14,439
if I go and take out every city's captain

171
00:07:14,439 --> 00:07:15,680
in a little while,

172
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,519
wouldn't that make us number one?

173
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:20,240
Is that realistic?

174
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:21,639
Is it not?

175
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:24,279
It's against the rules!

176
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:40,439
Qiushui City, Little Daoist

177
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:44,759
Here, sign over here

178
00:07:46,079 --> 00:07:46,839
Yes, yes, yes

179
00:07:47,399 --> 00:07:48,279
Just relax a bit more

180
00:07:48,399 --> 00:07:49,000
Good

181
00:07:54,759 --> 00:07:55,560
Very good, very good

182
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:56,600
Hello

183
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:58,839
Chuncao City, Liu Ruyan

184
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:03,680
Good

185
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:04,720
Look over here

186
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:05,720
Look at the camera

187
00:08:07,079 --> 00:08:07,839
Good, thank you

188
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:17,800
What a handsome little guy.

189
00:08:19,279 --> 00:08:20,439
How old are you?

190
00:08:20,439 --> 00:08:21,120
Thirteen.

191
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,439
Thirteen already.

192
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,399
Such a wonderful age.

193
00:08:32,159 --> 00:08:33,440
Did you come here alone?

194
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:33,960
Yes.

195
00:08:37,399 --> 00:08:39,279
So no one's around to play with you?

196
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,679
Wouldn't that be boring?

197
00:08:41,519 --> 00:08:42,879
If you're bored,

198
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:45,639
you can come to my room tonight.

199
00:08:47,159 --> 00:08:48,080
I'll keep you company.

200
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:50,320
Sis, can you act like a gorilla?

201
00:08:51,919 --> 00:08:53,080
Yesterday I went to see a play.

202
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:55,440
The man onstage played a gorilla so well.

203
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:56,879
I wanted to take him back.

204
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:59,639
But Young Master Geng wouldn't allow it.

205
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,600
Why take him back?

206
00:09:02,039 --> 00:09:03,080
He played the part so well.

207
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,679
But in the end, it's still human skin.

208
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:07,039
I can feel he was truly trying his best

209
00:09:07,039 --> 00:09:08,120
to play that gorilla well.

210
00:09:08,279 --> 00:09:08,879
So,

211
00:09:08,879 --> 00:09:11,159
just put him in a gorilla's skin and he can do it.

212
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:14,240
As they say, saving others is saving yourself.

213
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:15,879
So, sis,

214
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,159
do you have any wishes?

215
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:17,960
No.

216
00:09:18,279 --> 00:09:19,360
A body full of pure yang energy,

217
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:20,240
yet he's babbling nonsense

218
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:21,360
just like a lunatic.

219
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:23,080
A Blessed One's yang energy

220
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,919
is far stronger than an ordinary person's.

221
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:27,600
I was hoping, before the contest officially starts,

222
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:28,840
to swindle a few more suckers

223
00:09:28,919 --> 00:09:30,720
and maybe boost my power a notch.

224
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:33,639
Didn't expect to run into a psycho right away.

225
00:09:34,279 --> 00:09:36,399
Going on about human skin and gorilla skin.

226
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:41,120
Yang energy.

227
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:46,159
Hello.

228
00:09:46,399 --> 00:09:47,120
Su Yang,

229
00:09:47,759 --> 00:09:48,519
Shanhai City.

230
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:53,039
Here, thanks for your work.

231
00:09:53,879 --> 00:09:55,120
Such intense yang energy.

232
00:09:56,799 --> 00:09:57,679
Good, smile a bit more.

233
00:09:57,679 --> 00:09:59,360
They can't all be lunatics, can they?

234
00:10:02,679 --> 00:10:03,440
Hello.

235
00:10:03,879 --> 00:10:05,039
I'm not doing too well.

236
00:10:07,679 --> 00:10:09,080
What I mean is,

237
00:10:09,679 --> 00:10:10,960
I'm very happy to meet you.

238
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:14,240
How happy?

239
00:10:15,039 --> 00:10:16,159
It means...

240
00:10:17,919 --> 00:10:19,799
it means really, really happy.

241
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,240
So,

242
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,679
you think I look like a clown

243
00:10:22,799 --> 00:10:23,879
and seeing me makes you happy?

244
00:10:25,639 --> 00:10:26,320
No.

245
00:10:26,679 --> 00:10:27,840
Are you sick in the head?

246
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,200
How did you know?

247
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:30,799
Lunatics, they're all lunatics.

248
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:31,799
A bunch of lunatics.

249
00:10:31,799 --> 00:10:33,000
Yes, very good, look at the camera.

250
00:10:33,679 --> 00:10:34,919
Here, sign in over here.

251
00:10:35,759 --> 00:10:36,399
Frostwind City,

252
00:10:36,399 --> 00:10:37,000
Hello.

253
00:10:37,279 --> 00:10:38,120
Ning Wuqing.

254
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,159
I refuse to believe

255
00:10:46,399 --> 00:10:49,000
three idiots can show up in one room at once.

256
00:10:56,279 --> 00:10:56,879
Get lost.

257
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:58,919
Or die.

258
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:11,279
Idiots.

259
00:11:12,919 --> 00:11:14,039
A bunch of idiots.

260
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:16,440
I really should've checked the almanac today.

261
00:11:16,799 --> 00:11:19,000
Damn cripple, what an act.

262
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:20,480
When the cleaning girl was here,

263
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:21,919
why were you cowering like a dog?

264
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:27,919
Get up.

265
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:29,960
Get up!

266
00:11:31,159 --> 00:11:32,120
Now he's putting on an act.

267
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:33,799
Come on, let me record this.

268
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:36,840
Let her see your ugly true face.

269
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:44,440
Quite the performer.

270
00:11:44,919 --> 00:11:46,000
Yeah, yeah, very nice.

271
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:46,960
Good, look over here.

272
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:48,240
Great expression.

273
00:11:49,120 --> 00:11:50,080
You can relax a bit.

274
00:11:50,759 --> 00:11:51,360
Good.

275
00:11:51,399 --> 00:11:52,200
Can we try that angle?

276
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:53,000
Take a look, are you satisfied?

277
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:53,639
Thanks a lot.

278
00:11:54,879 --> 00:11:56,000
Nice work. Eyes to the left.

279
00:11:57,120 --> 00:11:57,840
Very good.

280
00:11:58,720 --> 00:11:59,759
Loosen up a bit more.

281
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:02,240
Yeah, great, great.

282
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:04,279
Okay, give me a smile.

283
00:12:04,279 --> 00:12:05,480
Are you secretly recording someone?

284
00:12:08,159 --> 00:12:08,960
A Taoist, huh.

285
00:12:09,679 --> 00:12:10,200
That's right.

286
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:11,600
Didn't your Tao teach you

287
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:13,240
not to meddle in others' business?

288
